Class IdentityChangeEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • sailpoint.tools.xml.AbstractXmlObject

        • sailpoint.object.IdentityChangeEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, sailpoint.tools.xml.PersistentXmlObject

    public class IdentityChangeEvent
extends AbstractChangeEvent<Identity>
    An event that gets fired when an identity is created/update/deleted during aggregation, refresh, or through the UI.
